&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;blog.dueutil.tech&#x2F;introducing-dueutil-pets&#x2F;#hp-mana&quot;&gt;HP &amp;amp; Mana&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
